Darkfate/Chamaleon::

Darkfate replied to Killfest "I have them... Don't worry." he opened 
his comm link "CHAMALEON!!!!!!"

"Yeeess sir" answered the bot.

"Where're you????!!!!" screamed the Dragon

"In cr's, sir, we have two bots class 3"

"I need you here, come!" said Darkfate "and bring all jet pack that 
we have in the base..."

"Yes sir" answered Chameleon and speakin to Blaze an Bullet "Follow 
me... the leader is speaking"

And Chameleon ran where jet pack were.
